Brute Force Stop (bfstop)
Joomla System Plugin
by Bernhard Froehler

This plugin is intended to hinder brute force login attempts to any Joomla! site.

For detailed instructions on how to use it, please browse to
https://github.com/codeling/bfstop/wiki

If you find any issues, please report them at
https://github.com/codeling/bfstop/issues

If you are interested in the source code, or want to contribute, the repository can be found under
https://github.com/codeling/bfstop

For any further questions, don't hesitate to contact me under
bfstop@bfroehler.info

